      <title>Andrew Left 合伙人 Choi 因推文交易遭美国证券交易委员会起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/andrew-left-associate-choi-sued-by-sec-for-trading-on-tweets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位帮助做空者安德鲁·莱夫特（Andrew Left）的投资顾问发现，他陷入困境的香橼研究公司（Citron Research）因涉嫌协助准备误导性的社交媒体帖子和研究报告而被美国证券交易委员会起诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/andrew-left-associate-choi-sued-by-sec-for-trading-on-tweets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 18:48:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长雷恩表示经济增长疲软可能加剧通货紧缩压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/ecb-s-rehn-says-weak-growth-could-increase-disinflation-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员奥利·雷恩表示，欧元区经济形势愈发严峻可能会加剧消费者价格增长放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/ecb-s-rehn-says-weak-growth-could-increase-disinflation-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EQT 董事长称地缘政治是首要担忧，而非利率上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/eqt-chair-says-geopolitics-risk-is-no-1-worry-not-higher-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[EQT AB 董事长康尼·琼森 (Conni Jonsson) 表示，目前世界的地缘政治紧张局势比借贷成本上升的问题更令其公司担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/eqt-chair-says-geopolitics-risk-is-no-1-worry-not-higher-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 17:35:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
